									<p>Tweedsmuir History Books, compiled by local branches of the Women's Institute, are a valuable resource for genealogists, historians, students, teachers, and anyone with an interest in local history.<br /><a href="http://www.greyroots.com/exhibitions/virtual-exhibits/tweedsmuirs/">See More...</a></p>
